    <h1 class="project-title">🍰 Dessertz</h1>

    <div class="sub-headline">
        A cloud-hosted celebration of global pastry, sweets, and confections — built on Microsoft Azure IaaS.
    </div>

    <div class="section-block">
        <div class="section-title"><span>01</span> // Project Description</div>
        <div class="proposal-full">
            <p><strong>Connecting Culture Through Sweetness</strong></p>
            <p>
                <strong>Dessertz</strong> is a cloud-based web platform dedicated to celebrating the extraordinary diversity of desserts, pastries, and sweet culinary traditions from cultures around the world. From the delicate layers of a French mille-feuille to the fragrant sweetness of Middle Eastern baklava, every dessert carries within it a story of heritage, community, and identity. This platform aims to bring those stories together in one accessible, beautifully presented digital space.
            </p>
            <p>
                The platform is hosted on <strong>Microsoft Azure</strong>, deployed on an <strong>Ubuntu 22.04 LTS</strong> virtual machine using the <strong>Apache HTTP Server</strong>. This infrastructure follows the Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS) model, giving full control over the server environment while leveraging the scalability and reliability of Azure's cloud ecosystem. The current deployment serves a static website, establishing the foundation upon which more complex features will be built.
            </p>
            <p>
                Planned features for future development include a <strong>Regional Dessert Explorer</strong>, allowing users to browse sweets by country or cultural region; a <strong>Recipe Library</strong> with step-by-step guides to recreating traditional confections at home; and a <strong>Cultural Stories</strong> section that dives into the history and meaning behind iconic desserts worldwide. A dynamic database backend and user account system are also planned for later iterations.
            </p>
            <p>
                Beyond the technical components, Dessertz serves a meaningful social purpose — making global food culture more discoverable and accessible to curious people everywhere. Food is one of the most universal forms of human connection, and desserts in particular represent celebration, comfort, and creativity across every society. By hosting this platform in the cloud, it becomes available to anyone, anywhere, at any time, reflecting the inclusive spirit the project is built upon.
            </p>
            <div class="word-count">~ 300 words</div>
